Package: jsql
Version: 0.144
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, openjdk-21
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/ron190/jsql-injection
Description: Lightweight database information finder from a server
 jSQL Injection is a lightweight application used to detect and
 exploit SQL injection vulnerabilities. It automates the process of
 finding database information from a target server.
